    public class Region
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Region>, java.io.Serializable
    Project #5 CS 2334, Section 10 April 22, 2014 A super class for geographic regions. Contains properties and methods common to all region objects Implements Serializable and Comparable.
